title: Hymenophyllum moorei
data: Hymenophyllum moorei is a rare species of filmy fern in the family Hymenophyllaceae. It is endemic to the high cloud forest at Mount Gower and Mount Lidgbird at Lord Howe Island. A small epiphytic fern found usually on tree trunks and fallen logs.[1] This Polypodiidae-related article is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it.
